            "notes": "Introduce the importance of metals in smartphone technology."
        },
        {
            "type": "content",
            "title": "Why Metals Are Essential in Smartphones",
            "subtitle": "Basic Functional Importance",
            "blocks": [
                {
                    "kind": "paragraph",
                    "text": "Metals are indispensable in smartphones because of their electrical, thermal, and mechanical properties. They enable efficient signal transmission, heat dissipation, and physical durability. Without metals, the compact and powerful design of modern smartphones would not be possible."
                },
                {
                    "kind": "bullets",
                    "items": [
                        "Excellent electrical conductivity",
                        "High strength and durability",
                        "Efficient heat management"
                    ]
                }
            ],
            "notes": "Explain the fundamental reasons metals are used."
        },
        {
