            "subtitle": "Elemental Diversity",
            "blocks": [
                {
                    "kind": "paragraph",
                    "text": "A typical smartphone contains more than 60 different chemical elements, many of which are metals. These metals are distributed across various components such as batteries, circuit boards, displays, and casings, highlighting the elemental complexity of mobile devices."
